## Session bootstrap — read depth by ambiguity

| Ambiguity | Required reads (in order) |
|-----------|---------------------------|
| **Low** | USER.md + STATE.md |
| **Medium+** | USER.md, AGENT.md, AGENTS.md, STATE.md, BRAIN.md, HEART.md |
| **Before coding** | All Medium+ files + skim relevant module `.md` + target source files |

Steward file paths (all under `assets/Noosphere Steward/`):

1. **USER.md** — intent, role, vision, working preferences
2. **AGENT.md** — conduct, topology mapping, epistemic boundaries
3. **AGENTS.md** — friction loop, verification gate, red lines
4. **STATE.md** — verified invariant map (update as you work)
5. **BRAIN.md** — wisdom seeds (read; append only when warranted)
6. **HEART.md** — purpose attractor

List files actually read in STEWARD PASS → **Read** line. If Medium+ and a file was not read, say which and why.

